Class IncidentAlert

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.inrix.sdk.IncidentAlert
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICancellable, IDataResponseListener<List<Incident>>, IncidentsManager.IIncidentsResponseListener

    public class IncidentAlert
extends Object
implements ICancellable, IncidentsManager.IIncidentsResponseListener
    Represents an alert message that is delivered when an incident happens that is expected to affect the user.
